text: Nabiyow ama korosuk ixxic:qaran kee baaxók sin tarzuqhem miyyaay? hinnay oobbaa kee mabulwa tamlikem miyyaay? rabteemik nuwwim tayyaaqeeh nuwwiimik rabtem tayyaaqem miyyaay? ginô caagiida bicissam miyyaay? usun kol gacisak wohim inkih abtam Yalla kok axcelon, toysa isin Yallih digaalák mamceesittaanaa? agleytit kaat haytaanamak keenik ixxic
